title: ADOPTABLE PET: Lucky Chi Dog Rescue
text:
Updated: 3:05 p.m. ADOPTABLE PET: Lucky Chi Dog Rescue More Dusty is available for adoption. COURTESY OF LUCKY CHI DOG RESCUE Related article » Animal’s Name: Dusty
Color: Brownish red
About the animal: This sweet boy will make a great lap dog, according to the rescue. He is so polite inside and will be a constant companion. The rescue also says one of his eyes doesn’t close completely, but the vet says he is fine. He is up to date on shots and fixed, housebroken and doggie door trained. He is also good with children and other dogs. He is an Animal Friends of the Valley Foster Dog.
Agency: Lucky Chi Dog Rescue
Location: Lake Elsinore/Perris area
Information: 951-544-6976, luckychidogres cue@aol.com, or visit Lucky Chi Dog Rescue on Facebook
Contact the writer: community@pe.com
